body:
I saw Endgame yesterday

Soo.. I saw Endgame yesterday. I cried. Me and my friend. We sobbed like crazy. This movie did things to my heart. It was funny, full of action but also so heartbreaking. I will see it again tomorrow and I will probably cry from the start. To everyone that is going to watch it: Good luck! Have fun! And here are some tissues for you!

title: 'Avengers: Endgame' - Last Minute Theories
body:
I wrote down some of my #AvengersEndgame fan theories before I watch the film TOMORROW. Who’s excited? *logs off twitter to avoid spoilers* #avengers #endgame #movie #marvel #mcu #blog

The time is 15:16. I am sitting at my laptop, shaking from head to toe, clenching my fists in protest of my Twitter addiction to avoid the inevitable onslaught of spoilers that plague my timeline. Tonight, at midnight, Avengers: Endgame will hit cinemas across the United Kingdom, and I am not ready.

A quick disclaimer: I’m not actually going to the midnight showing. I happen to work at my local…
